Localization.Name: Kastak Arms
Localization.Description: Kastak Arms makes inexpensive energy weapons with intimidating names like Devastator and Firestorm, and aggressively markets them to distressed parts of the Empire. Even though the company portrays itself as providing weapons for personal defense, the brand has become more readily identified with people who use them for aggressive and unlawful purposes.

Localization.Name: Custodian SMG
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Kastak Arms
Item Type: SMG
Class: Energy (Laser)

Battery Size: 60
Rate Of Fire: 800 rpm
Effective Range: 30 m

Attachments: Optics (S1), Barrel (S1), Underbarrel (S1)

The Custodian SMG from Kastak Arms focuses on a high rate of fire over damage and accuracy making it an ideal choice for sweeping through tight environments and close quarters combat.

Localization.Name: NV-TAC
Localization.Description: High-end company known for manufacturing technically precise and experimental optics and weapon attachments. Founded in 2811, NV-TAC initially built sensors for long-range scanning stations and surveying operations before shifting operations to the more profitable personal weapon market. Seen by some as too expensive and feature-dense, but beloved by soldiers and security professionals for their durable design, precision adjustments, and reliable performance.

Localization.Name: Gamma LL (1x Holographic)
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: NV-TAC
Type: Projection 
Attachment Point: Optic
Magnification: 1x
Aim Time: +15%
Size: 1

Whether under the blazing sun or on the dark side of a moon, the NV-TAC Gamma projects an easy to see reticle to help ensure your shot finds its mark. This version of the scope includes low-light functionality suitable for operations in dim environments.

Localization.Name: Veil Flash Hider3
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: ArmaMod
Type: Flash Hider
Attachment Point: Barrel
Size: 3

Localization.Name: Tracer Laser Pointer Green
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Klaus & Werner
Type: Laser Pointer
Attachment Point: Underbarrel
Size: 1

Spread: -12.5%

Trust Klaus & Werner to manufacture a tactical laser pointer that always hits the mark. The Tracer features a rust and impact resistant casing for an advanced laser diode that produces an efficient and stable beam. This special edition generates a green beam that's easy to see and identify.
